{"tid":1365930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發展局3年接1451宗涉「套丁」投訴　133宗轉交刑事調查","createTime":"2019-07-25T20:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T00:35:54.000Z","uid":165683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2c31793f4f730ddbac2fd622bda656bfce98a6bc","tid":1365930,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:11:32.000Z","msg":"過去有部分原居民濫用丁屋政策，目的只為「套丁」圖利。發展局回覆立法會議員查詢時表示，自2016至2018年的過去3年內，地政總署合共接獲1451宗舉報個案，指原居民涉嫌出售他們申建丁屋的權利，當中133宗懷疑個案經地政總署初步調查後，已轉交執法機構展開刑事調查。<br />\n現行丁屋政策容許原居村民在私人農地上申建丁屋，根據現時安排，地政總署處理在私人農地上興建丁屋的申請時，會要求申請人在法定聲明中，聲明是相關地段的唯一合法註冊業權人；小型屋宇建屋牌照亦要求持牌人，須保證從未與一人或多人訂定任何協議，以轉移或其他方式處理相關地段的權利。當中俗稱「套丁」的行為涉及有人以欺詐手段，在不符上述法定聲明或保證條款下，欺騙地政總署簽發小型屋宇批約或建屋牌照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190410/s00001/1554903726229/發展局3年接1451宗涉「套丁」投訴-133宗轉交刑事調查\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190410%2Fs00001%2F1554903726229%2F%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%B1%803%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A51451%E5%AE%97%E6%B6%89%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%97%E4%B8%81%E3%80%8D%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-133%E5%AE%97%E8%BD%89%E4%BA%A4%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hI26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=511d4f9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190410%2Fs00001%2F1554903726229%2F%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%B1%803%E5%B9%B4%E6%8E%A51451%E5%AE%97%E6%B6%89%E3%80%8C%E5%A5%97%E4%B8%81%E3%80%8D%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-133%E5%AE%97%E8%BD%89%E4%BA%A4%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5&h=e1a5164f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190410/s00001/1554903726229/發展局3年接1451宗涉「套丁」投訴-133宗轉交刑事調查</a>"},{"pid":"66a1139006504a16152ef694ef093f14e3b89596","tid":1365930,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:12:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7dM7QTB8ZnM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7dM7QTB8ZnM&d=VlhNwxbPYDbrmmiZclZ9hI26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=c953993e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7dM7QTB8ZnM</a>"},{"pid":"5da4e0281a184fbd281958995e2de8c4c4f1579f","tid":1365930,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:19:57.000Z","msg":"大家要做個好市民<br />\n知道嗎"},{"pid":"cedf917bf14dc1da1f775d8720169f40930f7857","tid":1365930,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:21:54.000Z","msg":"不偷舉報同投訴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfaac9430e026c2c3f6169cd56d1147ad79f8206","tid":1365930,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:32:15.000Z","msg":"1451投訴，133調查，0檢控？"},{"pid":"b404935277d6cf7837664b577cb49b48a4e32a66","tid":1365930,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:35:54.000Z","msg":"做個好市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}